Understanding the code


This application is very simple. It has only 4 files:




openvidu-browser-VERSION.js
: openvidu-browser library. You don't have to manipulate this file. 


app.js
: sample application main JavaScritp file, which makes use of 
openvidu-browser-VERSION.js
. You can manipulate this file to suit your needs.




index.html
: HTML code for the welcome page to join a new room and for the room itself. You can manipulate this file to suit your needs. It has two links to both JavaScript files: 


